def: Having two fingers or fingerlike projections.
That which is contained; the extent; the substance. [Obs.]The containment of a rich man's estate. Fuller.
A soldier enlisted for home service only; -- usually in the pl.
An oilskin hat or southwester; -- a fisherman's name. [U. S.]
Between the auricles; as, the interauricular partition of theheart.
A fossil leaf or impression of a leaf.
A place where a pin is fixed.
The act of recurring; return. [Obs.] Boyle.
Form or mode of construction; general figure; make; as, thebuild of a ship.
